  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A charming little shopkeeper accompanies you at all times.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/ad1f1c308e48fa149c925cb0dcee797c.poster.avif?t=1774514034\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/ad1f1c308e48fa149c925cb0dcee797c.webm?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/ad1f1c308e48fa149c925cb0dcee797c.mp4?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Raise fish in your carefully designed aquariums. Once they mature, choose to keep them close for steady gold income or exchange them for instant rewards.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/10c5cefc8827c13723383b6bf4460fb6.poster.avif?t=1774514034\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/10c5cefc8827c13723383b6bf4460fb6.webm?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/10c5cefc8827c13723383b6bf4460fb6.mp4?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover multiple themed aquariums filled with hundreds of hidden fish species and decors waiting to be uncovered.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/1619b68fa7c71577368b0f4946b0d045.poster.avif?t=1774514034\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/1619b68fa7c71577368b0f4946b0d045.webm?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/1619b68fa7c71577368b0f4946b0d045.mp4?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/b127f1ec7fa4283732e9820c65142532.poster.avif?t=1774514034\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/b127f1ec7fa4283732e9820c65142532.webm?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/b127f1ec7fa4283732e9820c65142532.mp4?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy a collection of over 10 sets of soft music accompanied by ambient white noise designed to help you relax, focus, and recharge while working or studying.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/f7bce3362b7f4b9d7ce91bce7f49546a.poster.avif?t=1774514034\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/f7bce3362b7f4b9d7ce91bce7f49546a.webm?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183350/extras/f7bce3362b7f4b9d7ce91bce7f49546a.mp4?t=1774514034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
